data.description: Nice updated home, 4-bedrooms, 2-bathrooms, 2 car garage, home has newer Roof (2 years old). New Tile Floors throughout, formal Living room, huge great room, formal dining room and breakfast nook. The kitchen has granite countertop and plenty cabinets, great bar/eat in area for high chairs, good size pantry for your convenience. It comes with all appliances. This split bedroom plan offers inside laundry with washer and dryer included. Windows treatment included and light fixtures, fan in all bedrooms. Master bedroom with walk-in closet and master bath with tile shower, guest bathroom with hot tub. Sliding doors that open up to a large screen-in porch. The backyard comes with fence for your pets and/or best use.This high desirable location home has No association. No fees. It comes with one year home warranty. Lot is .23 of acre.
